<p>In addition to competitive performance-related pay, Signature Flight Support offers the following benefits to team members based in Canada:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Generous Paid Time Off</li>
  <li>Attractive holiday allowance</li>
  <li>Comprehensive on-the-job training</li>
  <li>Advanced training and development opportunities</li>
  <li>Registered Retirement Savings Plan (RRSP)</li>
</ul>
